				'judul' => 'New Location of Bali Logam Mulia Gold Boutique',
				'deskripsi' => '<p style="margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.667em; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; margin-top: 0.6rem !important; margin-bottom: 0.6rem !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Denpasar, November 29, 2021</span>&nbsp;- PT Aneka Tambang Tbk (ANTAM; IDX: ANTM; ASX: ATM) member of Mining Industry Indonesia (MIND ID) – the State-Owned Enterprise Holding of the Mining Industry, is pleased to announce that the Company through its Precious Metal Processing and Refinery Business Unit, is relocating Bali Logam Mulia Gold Boutique to Jl Gatot Subroto Tengah no. 7, Dangin Puri Kaja, North Denpasar Distric, Denpasar – Bali, effective since Monday, November 29, 2021. The relocation of Bandung Logam Mulia Gold Boutique aimed to facilitate access and convenience in ANTAM\'s precious metals transaction for the customers from Bali and its surrounding. In the future, ANTAM expecting to boost the sales of ANTAM\'s precious metals where\'s located in one of the business centers in Bali.</p><p style="margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.667em; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; margin-top: 0.6rem !important; margin-bottom: 0.6rem !important;">Currently, customers can make direct transactions in Bali Logam Mulia Gold Boutique by implementing strict health protocols. Bali Logam Mulia Gold Boutique provides a&nbsp;<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">factory price promo for all ANTAM\'s precious metals products and free first year membership fee for Bronze type of BRANKAS LM from November 29 to December 4, 2021</span>. Through this promo is expected to attract more potential customers in Bali and its surrounding areas to invest in ANTAM\'s precious metals product.</p><p style="margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.667em; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; margin-top: 0.6rem !important; margin-bottom: 0.6rem !important;">As the only gold metal processing and refinery unit in Indonesia with London Bullion Market Association (LBMA) accreditation, ANTAM guarantees the products and quality of its precious metals. ANTAM also ensures the security and convenience of the transactions through the purchase of an online system, Logam Mulia Gold Boutique networks, or exhibition activities. The Company continuously appeals to all ANTAM\'s precious metals customers and the public to be cautious of the fraudulent mode of precious metal sales on behalf of ANTAM.</p><p style="margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.667em; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; margin-top: 0.6rem !important; margin-bottom: 0.6rem !important;">Further information about ANTAM\'s precious metals products can be seen at www.logammulia.com, social media Instagram @antamlogammulia, e-mail infolm@antam.com or call center 0804-1-888-888.</p>',
				'author' => 'Admin',
				'category' => 'News',
